name: Garwooken
content:
Garwooken was a male Wookiee, who lived during the waning years of the Galactic Republic. During the the SoroSuub Anniversary celebration in 31 BBY in the city Tolea Biqua on the planet Genarius, Garwooken was present in Vanster Enan's Cantina.
The miniature representing the character of Garwooken was based on a Wookiee concept sketch by Ralph McQuarrie.
